## EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

This consolidated dossier integrates two specialized intelligence operations:

**Layer 1 (v6.0.1):** Laptop acquisition + smartphone-compatible income generation  
**Layer 2 (v6.0.2):** Certifications, licenses, training programs, portfolio-building frameworks

**Combined strategic outcome:** Within 12 months, transition from reentry baseline to sustainable professional trajectory with multiple income pathways, verified credentials, and hireable technical portfolio.

**Key achievement targets:**
- Laptop acquisition (weeks 1–4)
- $300–$800/month income generation (months 1–3)
- Housing stability (months 1–3)
- Professional certification(s) earned (months 2–6)
- Hireable portfolio with 10+ projects (months 4–12)
- Career employment or advanced apprenticeship (months 6–12)

