**Task 9.3 — Remotasks Microtask Platform**

**Platform:** AI training task distribution  
**Device Access:** Full smartphone support  
**Cost:** Free  
**Barrier to Entry:** Extremely low  
**Payout Schedule:** Weekly (no minimum)  
**Time to First Earnings:** 1–2 days  

**Task Types:**
- Image labeling/annotation ($5–$15/hour)
- Data categorization ($5–$12/hour)
- Transcription snippets ($0.30–$1/minute)
- Simple research tasks ($8–$15/hour)

