2. Complete qualification tests (2–3 sample tasks)
3. Browse available tasks (refresh multiple times daily for best options)
4. Focus on image labeling/categorization initially
5. Work 1–2 hours daily for consistent $50–$100/week income

**Realistic Income:** $200–$400/month at 5–10 hours weekly

**Priority Index:** 8.2/10

