- Realistic: Complete content free via audit; pay $49 for 1 month to take graded exams

**Career Value:** Entry-level IT help desk roles ($35K–$50K+); Google-backed credential

**Eligibility:** Open to anyone

**Action Plan:**
1. Enroll on Coursera in audit mode (free)
2. Work through 4 courses over 4–6 weeks
3. Complete all practice labs
4. Final week: Apply for Coursera financial aid
5. If approved: Receive free exam voucher
6. If denied: Pay $49 for 1-month full access
7. Pass certification exams

**Priority Index:** 8.8/10

