1. Register at aws.amazon.com/education/awseducate
2. Complete AWS Educate Badge Course
3. Enroll in AWS Emerging Talent Community
4. Start AWS Skill Builder courses (Cloud Practitioner path)
5. Complete hands-on labs (free, no credit card)
6. Earn points by completing training + projects
