#### **Certification B.3 — Microsoft Azure Fundamentals (AZ-900)**

**Certification:** Microsoft Azure Fundamentals (AZ-900)  
**Cost:** FREE vouchers available via multiple channels  
**Exam Fee (if paid):** $99 USD  

**Free Voucher Methods:**

**Option 1: Microsoft Virtual Training Day (Recommended)**
- Attend free 2-day Microsoft Virtual Training Day on Azure Fundamentals
- Receive 50% discount OR free voucher (varies by event)
- Check Microsoft Learn Events page for next event

**Option 2: Student Pricing (If at PCC)**
- Use student email to verify status on Microsoft Learn
- Access free or heavily discounted AZ-900 exam through academic pricing
- Some institutions provide full free access for students

**Option 3: Microsoft Learn (Free Training Only)**
- Complete AZ-900 learning modules on Microsoft Learn (FREE)
- Content is comprehensive

**Why Azure Matters:** Cloud computing is mandatory. Azure Fundamentals validates foundational cloud knowledge. Salary range: $70K–$95K for Azure Administrator roles.

**Content:** Cloud concepts, Azure services, solutions, management & governance

**Action Plan:**
1. Enroll at Microsoft Learn (free account)
2. Set student status + verify with PCC email (if applicable)
3. Check Microsoft Learn Events for next Virtual Training Day
4. Register for free event (limited spots; register early)
5. Attend both days of training
6. Claim free/discounted exam voucher
7. Complete Microsoft Learn AZ-900 learning path (35+ hours free)
8. Schedule exam with Pearson VUE
9. Pass exam (65% passing score threshold)

**Priority Index:** 8.4/10

