## RISK MITIGATION & CONTINGENCIES

| Risk | Contingency Plan |
|------|---|
| Free Geek inventory limited | Apply to PCs for People + Computers with Causes simultaneously |
| Upwork early rejection | Start Remotasks + Rev immediately; build reviews first |
| Housing wait-list long | Seek emergency assistance through WorkSource; contact local nonprofits |
| Pell Grant delays | Proceed with college enrollment; grants retroactively applied |
| Computer lab access slow | Prioritize laptop acquisition; use library wifi |
| Music projects slow | Focus on general freelance (Upwork VA, writing); supplement with beat production |
| Next Chapter rejection | Pursue Codecademy + freelance dev path; reapply following cohort |
| Apprenticeship pool wait | Continue income generation + certification building during wait |

